OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776672340
OL,3,CMotability scheme users face 'admin
OL,4,Cfee' for cross-border travel
OL,6,FA woman from Fermanagh has told UTV
OL,7,Fthat she's anxious her quality of life
OL,8,Fmight shrink if plans to change a UK-
OL,9,Fwide disability scheme go ahead.
OL,11,FThe Motability Scheme allows people
OL,12,Fwho qualify for mobility allowances to
OL,13,Flease a vehicle. It means Sarah
OL,14,FGriffiths, one of the Motability
OL,15,FScheme users, can travel in a
OL,16,Fspecially adapted van with her family.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776672340
OL,3,CMotability scheme users face 'admin
OL,4,Cfee' for cross-border travel
OL,6,F"Motability scheme has been
OL,7,Ftransformational for our family.
OL,8,FBefore I got this chair and use the
OL,9,Fvan, we used to go out on a manual
OL,10,Fchair and I couldn't push myself,"
OL,11,FSarah said.
OL,13,FHowever, from July, a number of
OL,14,Fchanges are being introduced for all
OL,15,Fnew leases. The amount of mileage
OL,16,Fcovered each year is being halved -
OL,17,Fdown to 10,000. Any journeys beyond
OL,18,Fthat distance will cost 25p a mile, up
OL,19,Ffrom 5p," she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776672340
OL,3,CMotability scheme users face 'admin
OL,4,Cfee' for cross-border travel
OL,6,FBeing from the countryside, Sarah says
OL,7,Fshe'll exceed the 10,000 miles a year.
OL,8,FAs a result, once she needs a new
OL,9,Flease, she said her family may have to
OL,10,Fthink twice before taking certain
OL,11,Fjourneys.
OL,13,F"It would be cost-prohibitive and it
OL,14,Fwould have a huge impact on our
OL,15,Fquality of life," she said.
OL,17,FCustomers were told about the changes
OL,18,Fby email, but Sarah feels they should
OL,19,Fhave been consulted beforehand.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776672340
OL,3,CMotability scheme users face 'admin
OL,4,Cfee' for cross-border travel
OL,6,FAsked how she felt when reading the
OL,7,Fmessage informing her about the
OL,8,Fdecision, she said: "That's
OL,9,Fpatronising."
OL,11,FCross-border journeys will also be
OL,12,Faffected by changes.
OL,14,FFrom July, people will have to pay an
OL,15,Fadmin fee before travelling to the
OL,16,FRepublic as it's in the EU. The exact
OL,17,Ffigure hasn't been released yet but
OL,18,FUTV understands it'll be around 20
OL,19,Fpounds a year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
