PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776672340
OL,3,CMotability scheme users face 'admin
OL,4,Cfee' for cross-border travel
OL,6,FIn a statement, Motability Operations
OL,7,Fsaid last year's tax changes have made
OL,8,Frunning the scheme more expensive.
OL,10,FIt added: "Around 3 in 4 people who
OL,11,Fuse the scheme travel within the
OL,12,Fmileage allowance" and that "any
OL,13,Fadditional mileage is charged at a
OL,14,Frate that reflects the real cost of
OL,15,Fhigher use".
